{"title":"海岸上的花朵的颂歌","authors":["巴勃罗·聂鲁达"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海岸上的花朵的颂歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔智利〕巴勃罗·聂鲁达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多野花开放在黑岛上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们没有名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的像雪一样洁白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的摇荡着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像黄色的火焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个乡村的诗人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像猎人一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜在海边燃起一堆野火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的周围是空旷的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的旁边是你，——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愉快、单纯——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一朵玫瑰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，生活——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它呼唤我去战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了复活大地上的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是人们的兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由于爱与责任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的双手才这样坚强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在海岸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩石中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见开着花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们久久地等待着冬天的结束，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好把芳香赠给春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，我要告别（这是第几次啊！）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枯枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砂土，——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不忍离去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我是一个乡村的诗人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由于爱与责任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，双手才这样坚强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（孙玮　译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}